<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.9.7">
<l>peṟṟārpeṟ ṟoḻintār piṉṉumniṉ ṟaṭiyēṉuk</l>
<l>kuṟṟāṉāy vaḷartteṉ ṉuyirā kiniṉṟāṉai</l>
<l>muṟṟāmā matikōḷ viṭuttā ṉaiyemmāṉai</l>
<l>yettālyāṉ maṟakkē ṉitucol leṉēḻaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>How could I forget the one who endures as my life,</l>
<l>Nurturing [me], remaining as a beloved to me, his servant,</l>
<l>After [my] parents bore [me] and left, our lord, the one who split</l>
<l>The serpent of the great incomplete moon? Tell [me] this, my simple heart!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
